Install and configure Apache2 package in your server.


-> apt install apache2 -y


-> a2enmod ssl && a2ensite default-ssl.conf


-> nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/default-ssl.conf
#Change DocumentRoot para htmls.
#Change certificate name.


-> rm /var/www/html/index.html && nano /var/www/html/index.html
#Type something like: "Welcome to my server on port 80!"


-> mkdir /var/www/htmls && nano /var/www/htmls/index.html
#Type something like: "Welcome to my server on port 443!"


-> systemctl restart apache2
